Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P314  Footwear, Ex Rubber.
    P2323 Men's and Boys' Neckwear.
    P3171 Women's Handbags and Purses.
    P3161 Luggage.
    P3873 Watches, Clocks, Watchcases and Parts.
    P3711 Motor Vehicles and Car Bodies.
</IN>
